manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: 10 ft length is long enough to reach across a room It's long enough so you could be comfortable lying on the couch or bed , it is plugged in behind your bed and never have to worry about plugging not charging your phone or charger not reaching,10 foot cord is fantastic when you are charging phone at a distance from outlet. Apple MFI-Certified iPhone Charger 10 ft MFI Certified by Apple without warning message pops up.Original MFI lighting cable chip 8 Pin connector with a lightning end,quicker and safer than other cheaper lightning cable. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 12, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great Durability for Quadriplegics
reviews.reviewText: I highly recommend this charging cord for people with disabilities! With no use of my fingers, the angle is much easier for me to “mash” into the iPad or iPhone. IYKYK 😂 The length is great for reaching across the bed. It is also FAST charging! …. even great for charging iPads that often seem to take more power. This cord lasts longer than any other cord I’ve tried. I hope you find this information useful!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 17, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice economic chargers
reviews.reviewText: These chargers are really nice for their price. I like using both styles of chargers. These ones are better if you have problems with the wire splitting on your phone near the charging port. After time, these tend to wear down and don’t seem to charge as fast.. but you get your use of them.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 26, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Right angle cord helps to prevent the cord from fraying and the price makes it a good value. The cord is sturdier than many I have owned, also. Highly recommend.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 14, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars I like it but…
reviews.reviewText: Honestly I really like this product, it’s got to be my favorite charger out of all I got, I used it for a long time till it broke by the charger head coming apart, and I gave the other pairs away so I bought more just because I liked it so much. I had always had the problem with the weird twisty cable thing and the sometimes when you pull you gotta replug it as well to make it charge but I still like it. Though this one I got not too long ago and it twisted hard a couple days after I got it. Look at the picture, can’t unfold it and it still works so I guess it’s still good.Update : it’s June 14th and this cable no longer works correctly, it lasted 83 days and I assumed it stopped working because of how bendy it is 🥺.
